If you dont provide the storage account while creating metastore, you will be creating catalog for every workspace then you have to provide the storage location . The best practice recommedation is to always attah storage location to your Unity Metastore.
How will the metastore will be able to read and write the data to datalake? - It is via access connector. It will have the access to this data lake with access of storage blob contributor and and we will use this connector in this metastore to access this data lake. 

